      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/data/fda-generic-pump-experimental-dataset",
      "type": "uofa:Dataset",
      "name": "FDA generic centrifugal blood pump experimental hemolysis dataset",
      "uofa:isFoundationalEvidence": true,
      "description": "Experimentally measured normalised index of hemolysis (NIH) values for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump across a matrix of flow rates (2–7 L/min) and rotational speeds (2000–3500 RPM), collected under ISO 10993-4 compliant in-vitro conditions."
    },
