      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty (turbulence model selection, hemolysis damage model) not formally assessed at MRL 2. k-omega SST turbulence model selected based on published benchmark performance for pump flows. Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis model used per community consensus."
